Uses of Package
icap.core

Packages that use icap.core
icap Overall ICAP package. 
icap.core Core ICAP processing features: statics, protocol parser and abstraction layer for fast services development 
icap.services ICAP Services implementation. 
icap.services.resources.gs icap services specific resources 
tools.httpserver.custom Specific pages adaptation for GreasySpoon administration 
 

Classes in icap.core used by icap
AbstractService
          Abstract class silently providing all ICAP protocol parsing methods for both REQ and RESPMODE
Services implementation must just provide getResponse() and getOptions() methods
Icap
          Generic interface used to define ICAP constants
 

Classes in icap.core used by icap.core
Icap
          Generic interface used to define ICAP constants
Icap.ClientBrand
          Defines ICAP client brand to allow custom implementation/optimisations
Icap.TYPE
          Defines ICAP requests type that can be received
Icap.VectoringPoint
          Vectoring points that can be supported by a service: REQMOD, RESPMOD or both
IcapParser
          ICAP protocol parser.
Determine ICAP request type (OPTIONS/REQMOD/RESPMOD), parse ICAP request and embedded HTTP messages for REQMOD and RESPMOD.
